Invaders from the Strange Space (ISS) is a clone of Space Invaders but slightly different and with more features.

Build 47 - Public Beta

NEW FEATURES

- Improved Main Menu.
- Changed resolution from 800x600 to 640x480.
- Score is now calculated by the kills, accuracy and remaining life of the player.
- Mouse can be enabled from the settings.
- From pause the player is able to return to the main menu.
- Players' health is now a visual graphic.
- Added a settings menu.
- Added a highscore screen.
- Players can now mute the sound.
- Performance improvements.
- Redesigned levels.